summary: Both REQ-9 and REQ-10 are well-implemented. A new PrayerTimings.tsx page was created with all 30 days of static prayer times, Arabic and English prayer names, Islamic green and gold theme, and mobile-first layout. App.tsx was updated with the /prayer-timings route, and Home.tsx was updated with a navigation card for Ramadan Prayer Timings. No missing requirements or hallucinated features were identified.
